From 2a12efc567a270a155e3b886258297abd79cdea0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Richard Zhu <hongxing.zhu@nxp.com>
Date: Tue, 26 Nov 2024 15:56:56 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 044/133] PCI: imx6: Skip controller_id generation logic for
 i.MX7D
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

[ Upstream commit f068ffdd034c93f0c768acdc87d4d2d7023c1379 ]

